            "title": "傅里葉IPO在港售股超購3117倍 下限定價暗盤高收逾倍 銅師傅暗盤潛水",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">今日再有兩隻新股掛牌，其中半導體板塊的傅里葉(03625)在港售股獲3118.43倍認購，以下限每股40元定價，昨天暗盤大幅高收逾倍。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"傅里葉半導體\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/FS-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"傅里葉半導體\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/FS-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">傅里葉半導體</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">輝立交易平台顯示，傅里葉暗盤收報84.6元，較招股價高1.12倍；富途交易平台顯示暗盤則收報83.5元，高於招股價1.09倍。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該股IPO在港公開發售部份1手中籤率5%，國際配售獲2.93倍認購。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：銅師傅文創官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260311_FI_source-web_Tongshifu-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：銅師傅文創官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260311_FI_source-web_Tongshifu-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：銅師傅文創官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">同樣在今日登場的銅師傅(00664)，亦以下限每股60元定價；在港公開售股獲59.55倍認購，1日中籤率2.78%，國際配售認購1.56倍。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該股昨天暗盤表現則與傅里葉迥異，富途交易平台顯示銅師傅昨天暗盤收報41.96元，較招股價低30.1%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15815939-%e5%82%85%e9%87%8c%e8%91%89ipo%e5%9c%a8%e6%b8%af%e5%94%ae%e8%82%a1%e8%b6%85%e8%b3%bc3117%e5%80%8d-%e4%b8%8b%e9%99%90%e5%ae%9a%e5%83%b9%e6%9a%97%e7%9b%a4%e9%ab%98%e6%94%b6%e9%80%be%e5%80%8d-%e9%8a%85",
