            "title": "黑期低期均低水逾近70點 重磅港股ADR跌多於升",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">新加坡黑期於今早約8時10分跌56點或0.23%，報24682點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股ADR指數報24675點，較香港上日現貨收市低74點或0.3%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合每股港幣478.2元，較上日香港收市低3.43元或0.71%；阿里巴巴(09988)ADR收市折合每股港幣119.5元，較上日香港收市低1.04元或0.86%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美團(03690)ADR收市折合每股港幣84元，較上日香港收市低0.17元或0.2%；京東(09618)ADR收市折合每股港幣113.4元，較上日香港收市高0.37元或0.3%；小米(01810)ADR收市折合每股港幣31.9元，較上日香港收市低0.44元或1.37%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：騰訊官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滙控(00005)ADR收市折合每股港幣124.3元，較上日香港收市高0.74元或0.6%；友邦(01299)ADR收市折合每股港幣85元，較上日香港收市高0.05元或0.06%；港交所(00388)ADR收市折合每股港幣380.7元，較上日香港收市低1.7元或0.44%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中國平安(02318)ADR收市折合每股港幣58.4元，較上日香港收市低0.45元或0.77%；建設銀行(00939)ADR收市折合每股港幣8.2元，較上日香港收市低0.04元或0.5%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">4月份恒指期貨夜市收報24683點，跌61點，較上日恒指收市24750點，低水68點。科指期貨夜市收報4662點，較上日科指收市低水28點；國指期貨夜市收報8372點，較上日國指收市低水27點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15815931-%e9%bb%91%e6%9c%9f%e4%bd%8e%e6%9c%9f%e5%9d%87%e4%bd%8e%e6%b0%b4%e9%80%be%e8%bf%9170%e9%bb%9e-%e9%87%8d%e7%a3%85%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1adr%e8%b7%8c%e5%a4%9a%e6%96%bc%e5%8d%87",
